WEBVTT

00:08:28.733 --> 00:08:30.566
is not just a roof.

00:08:30.590 --> 00:08:31.811
It's more than a roof.

00:08:31.835 --> 00:08:33.236
It's telling a story;

00:08:33.260 --> 00:08:37.766
it's telling a story about the identity
of the people living in that hut.

00:08:38.427 --> 00:08:39.577
Individuals.

00:08:40.109 --> 00:08:43.355
Architecture is the art
of telling stories.

00:08:44.212 --> 00:08:45.545
Like this one.

00:08:46.530 --> 00:08:48.918
In London: the Shard of Glass.

00:08:48.942 --> 00:08:53.635
Well, this building is the tallest
building in Western Europe.

00:08:54.013 --> 00:08:59.403
It goes up more than 300 meters
in the air, to breathe fresh air.

00:08:59.427 --> 00:09:03.172
The facets of this building are inclined,